    {
      "start": 203.11,
      "end": 204.67,
      "text": "So what did he say?"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.81,
      "end": 205.53,
      "text": "뭐라고 했었냐면"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.53,
      "end": 207.21,
      "text": "기분 안 좋을 때"
